      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 17:13:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔表示美联储在决定降息之前有时间评估数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/powell-says-fed-has-time-to-assess-data-before-deciding-to-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，政策制定者将等待通胀下降的更明显迹象，然后再降息，尽管最近的物价上涨并没有改变其更广泛的轨迹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/powell-says-fed-has-time-to-assess-data-before-deciding-to-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 16:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
